Notes:

1. A.E.L.U. stands for Asociación Estadio La Unión.
2. Sporting Cristal B can´t be promoted as they are the "second team" of Sporting Cristal which
   plays in First Division. Sporting Cristal B was previously known as Sport Agustino.
3. Before the tournament´s start, Meteor abandonned the competition. So we have 12 teams
   instead of 13.
4. On Round 1 the match Yurimaguas-Vigo originally ended, but later Yurimaguas was declared
   winner by 2-0


Promotion Playoff [Dec 18, Lima]
América Cochahuayco - Deportivo Pesquero    2-2 [aet, 3-4 pen]
 [Carrión 45' Ibarra 72' / Espinoza 60' Silvera 61']

América Cochahuayco remains in Segunda Division for 2000.


